Invocation Name: multiplication teacher
des:
Multiplication teacher is a skill that allows you to practice your multiplication tables. You can begin by saying "Alexa, multiplication teacher".
The skill will then ask which multiplication table you want to practice.
For example "Practice multiplication by two" will ask you 10 questions around the table of 2.
At the end you'll get a score to know how many good answers you got.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
